<A>__{suitcase in hand, yuri surveys his bedroom for the last time. a car horn. he glances through the window to the communist style plaza below. anatoly beckons impatiently to yuri. vitaly and irina load overstuffed suitcases into an old russian sedan driven by an old russian military officer, uncle dmitri. yuri stares at himself in the mirror. he replaces his stolen soviet pin for a necklace a star of david.}
